{"tid":864111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【返工大混亂@中環】OL返新工第二日遲到 憂上司留壞印象","createTime":"2018-10-16T03:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T08:05:02.000Z","uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2c48a6c8a50109848252d1c831fdb954b346fd","tid":864111,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"【返工大混亂@中環】OL返新工第二日遲到 憂上司留壞印象<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181016/large/1539654812_0d44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181016%2Flarge%2F1539654812_0d44.jpg&h=d1efda50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女乘客Eve（右圖）指今日第二日上新工，擔心上司對她留下壞印象。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵荃灣綫、觀塘綫及港島綫，今晨同時出現信號故障，連帶將軍澳綫的行車時間也受影響。<br />\n早上8時10分，中環站人頭湧湧。職員在香港站與中環站之間的位置拉起封鎖線，又暫停電動通道，現場估計聚集近千人，部份人鼓譟。<br />\n女乘客Eve指，新工第二日上班，因為天雨已經預早時間出門口，不料發生信號故障，肯定要遲到了，擔心上司對她留下壞印象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181016/58799214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58799214&d=MCtIC93QByPSCqUAHvyvccmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=073936d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58799214&h=6f982fbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181016/58799214</a>"},{"pid":"a0851c89df49c9134358662ce84b7e865c76c8de","tid":864111,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"send返條link俾上司睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b67b66fc26cee274689760ad4b84d2969c37b3","tid":864111,"uid":122134,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老母....<br />\n香港人真係返工返到傻<br />\n咁撚大條道理都要驚<br />\n如果佢老細咁都屌..證明佢老細都係條濕9<br />\n我想問佢..如果佢公司比人炸左 <br />\n佢係咪都會係&quot;啞嚦&quot;中工作"},{"pid":"025504382547af6d8ca4dfa3c40a123d358fad08","tid":864111,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"全世界都返唔到工，你唔係諗住你上司可以返到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非上司住公司附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96c729ec02fc594c9310061087f720a7a6a6a42","tid":864111,"uid":135957,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b422d6be01e775d79773f817618f4ce7fe5caa5","tid":864111,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"六點鍾通知大家故障<br />\n上司：點解唔識提早出門口，有必要員工應在公司留宿"}]}